ile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T19:34:30.000Z","msg":"以前年紀細 咩都外貌行先<br />\n<br />\n而家人大咗 心態開始變<br />\n<br />\n只係想有個相處得舒服 唔使點講都明對方嘅伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:22:35.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n但真係好能難搵啊"},{"pid":"4d2d105a8c23ca24ccdd05522a8b3b9a821c96f9","tid":698543,"uid":150698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"啲男人承諾完做唔到<br />\n唔該唔好承諾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fc56be64cc5396a7974b7e716415a54c6feb7c","tid":698543,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"739dc335d16965862fc240661aee88a9ee4a003f","tid":698543,"uid":137491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4091c646c1ca4dae7d0159e7ea87d3460402ab28","tid":698543,"uid":140597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T19:18:13.000Z","msg":"會有一點荒謬嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人每次拍拖 都盼望自己女朋友第時會變做老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T19:20:49.000Z","msg":"初戀都應承過娶我<br />\n依家...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"香港同性婚姻未合法 等吓啦"},{"pid":"1737d21d92f0a96412dc292d9670e7f5c8d5564b","tid":698543,"uid":103310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d2d105a8c23ca24ccdd05522a8b3b9a821c96f9","tid":698543,"uid":150698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"啲男人承諾完做唔到<br />\n唔該唔好承諾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"而家我承諾左，佢唔想比我履行承諾咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />